{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM08_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x15,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong? You seem like you're in a bad mood."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "...Oh really. How so?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You really are in a bad mood..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry, it seems to be affecting my attitude."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "What's wrong? It's unusual to see you in such a bad mood, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...It's about where Luard went. No matter how much I investigate it, I can find no clues."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "You're also working very hard at your alchemy, but it's frustrating that I still can't remember."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, Plachta? Why is Luard using Ablation Alchemy, anyway?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Luard has been enthralled by the power of Ablation Alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "In the past, Luard conducted fairly normal alchemy research for a certain goal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "But at one point, he discovered Ablation Alchemy, and blinded by its immense power, he forgot his original goals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "It's likely that Luard can only think about researching Ablation Alchemy now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It's true that Ablation Alchemy holds great power."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "If the cost problems associated with it could be resolved, it could even be the ideal form of alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "However, in reality, the costs are far too great. Luard simply ignores that fact."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "He completely disregards the future risks. We cannot allow Luard to continue his reckless use of Ablation Alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I need to stop Luard, no matter what it takes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(I was wondering before, but Plachta seems to look really sad whenever she talks about Luard...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "(I wonder why...)"
        }
    ]
}